{"id": "1458832727334981735", "channel_id": "1326453763355185215", "type": 0, "author_id": "212031841786527764", "author_name": "chinkeeyong", "author_bot": false, "content": "I found a semaphore alphabet chart and decided to look up what corposant is actually signalling with each of her animations\n\nStrike: L - Lima - Stop immediately\nDefense: V - Victor - I require assistance\nOminous Semaphore: Y - Yankee - I am dragging my anchor\nPilot: same as Defense\n\nher Ominous Semaphore line is \"Echo, stand by for instructions\" but she isn't actually signalling E in any of her animations <:scared2:1356085635374383145> (and also that's not what Echo means)\n\nlikewise one of her Pilot lines is \"Charlie, acknowledged\" but she never signals C", "timestamp": "2026-01-08T14:40:25.998000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-01-08T14:40:57.468000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
